chore(vscode-webui): clean i18n prompt placeholder improvements

Apply improved i18n translations for prompt placeholder:
- English: "Ask anything..." 
- Japanese: "何でもお聞きください..." (polite/welcoming)
- Korean: "무엇이든 물어보세요..." (natural Korean)
- Chinese: "问我任何问题..." (conversational tone)

This commit provides a clean implementation without merge complexity.

